         MACRO
         TIMEDIT &WORK,&OUTPUT
*.
* TIMEDIT MACRO INSTRUCTION. PUT THE TIME OF DAY AS HH.MM.SS OUT
* IN SAPIEN-READABLE FORMAT.
*
* VARIABLES -
*        WORK    FULLWORD DEFINED FOR WORKING STORAGE (RX ADDRESS)
*        OUTPUT  NINE-BYTES DEFINED FOR OUTPUT EDITING. THE LAST
*                EIGHT ARE VALID, THE FIRST IS THE PAD CHARACTER
*.
         TIME  DEC
         ST    R0,&WORK
         MVC   &OUTPUT.(9),=X'4021204B20204B2020'
         ED    &OUTPUT.(9),&WORK
         MEND
